Are you pushing it?

00:04.838 --> 00:07.908
Push it!
I have fingers!
It just goes, "Bing."

00:07.941 --> 00:10.678
(chiming)
Is it "bing"
or "bing?"

00:10.711 --> 00:12.513
Bing. Bing.
It's a bad bing.

00:12.546 --> 00:14.082
Makes the sound of
terminal cancer,

00:14.115 --> 00:16.384
or my mother pressing me
for an intimate lunch.

00:16.417 --> 00:18.819
Got it.
Is this video thingy gonna work
now? 'Cause it's important.

00:18.852 --> 00:20.554
You like these shoes?
You bought 'em

00:20.588 --> 00:22.423
