00:22.456 --> 00:24.225
Now you can eat the leaves
at the top of the tree.

00:24.258 --> 00:27.895
Half giraffe,
half drag queen, honey.

00:27.928 --> 00:31.365
Hi. It's me, Bryan Collins.

00:31.399 --> 00:33.867
But you won't know me as that.

00:33.901 --> 00:36.737
You will know me as... Dad.

00:37.905 --> 00:39.773
Maybe even Daddy.

00:42.576 --> 00:46.214
Oh, God, I think I would just
die if you called me Daddy.

00:46.247 --> 00:48.382
Um...

00:48.416 --> 00:52.853
this video is to show you...

00:52.886 --> 00:55.789
