forget this time?
My name tag.

01:51.312 --> 01:53.481
I need it for work.
I don't understand.

01:53.514 --> 01:55.283
You were always so pretty.

01:55.316 --> 01:57.651
You got knocked up.
You pissed it all away.

01:57.685 --> 01:59.253
