back there, so...

02:53.841 --> 02:56.277
Oh, and, um... one last thing?

02:57.845 --> 02:59.913
I've kind of given up
on my life.

02:59.947 --> 03:01.682
I forgot I want it all.

03:01.715 --> 03:04.718
This was the last push I needed
to remember that, so thank you.

03:05.753 --> 03:07.655
Congratulations.

03:07.688 --> 03:10.458
He's all yours.

03:12.293 --> 03:14.428
So, are you thinking
about joining

03:14.462 --> 03:16.664
